opp_guild_info.comment: Be nice and friendly, ask questions and share tips and advice in guild chat. Selfish play, cheating and inactivity will get you kicked. Play the game for fun, take your time to improve and use your swords with pride!
opp_guild_info.notice: Pls set your gw defense and give your best these final wars
opp_guild_info.name: Our Truth

guild_info.comment: (=ﾟωﾟ)ﾉ ヽ(´o｀) Hello! Please notice that you have to be active and use all of your swords (Win/Lose/Draw) to help contribute to guild battles. Thank you! ( ´ ▽ ` )ﾉ
